{"tid":665501,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"不sir的攝影評論分享","createTime":"2018-05-15T04:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T14:08:55.000Z","uid":11779,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fa375be3f063d818615b480ac19ddcb088686412","tid":665501,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/121612_fd6c5bddc33928baedc0965defa55904.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F121612_fd6c5bddc33928baedc0965defa55904.jpeg&h=22d79ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係我不sir, 今日想同大家分享呢幅偉大作品，如果大家留意地下 就知個對焦係係對新人前一尺左右。<br />\n<br />\n令我諗起小學雞用菲林時唔識對焦比師傅屌時嘅回憶。攝影師係21世界攝影器材咁精準嘅情況下依然可以將個對焦對前一尺製做出藝術家先識欣賞嘅lomo效果，令日十分敬佩。<br />\n<br />\n致於你地覺得好唔好就等你地自己決定。但我覺得一定影行好好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355a4a969183c1e781a4280638bbd7874040b39a","tid":665501,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"正評影得好 負皮唔好。"},{"pid":"fa6663885849113533a98bbb9d20f70b9ce3f155","tid":665501,"uid":163554,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ecf35f881a364884379be8aac237e26edf6e099","tid":665501,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"fa6663885849113533a98bbb9d20f70b9ce3f155","tid":665501,"uid":163554,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"我真心覺得靚喎，our focus得好夢幻。"},{"pid":"0975a2b4c5c7576fe40c5930293489793e8e2e22","tid":665501,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8ecf35f881a364884379be8aac237e26edf6e099","tid":665501,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"fa6663885849113533a98bbb9d20f70b9ce3f155","tid":665501,"uid":163554,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyT